{"tid":2311880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台北捷運廁所設限時裝置：15分鐘通報站務員關心、30分鐘響警報　高鐵：無障礙廁所4分鐘響警報！","createTime":"2020-12-04T11:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T17:15:44.000Z","uid":209657,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ced03d66007b0097d89b0d7edcbcd61ca9c7196b","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/11/28/realtime/9157358.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=60&amp;y=0&amp;sw=1141&amp;sh=856&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F11%2F28%2Frealtime%2F9157358.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D60%26y%3D0%26sw%3D1141%26sh%3D856%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D800&h=f1d8429a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如廁要限時？台北捷運的廁所首開先例，若在廁間超過十五分鐘，可能會有站務人員來關心，逾三十分鐘警報器會響起。北捷表示，這項作法用意在適時協助民眾、確保安全，高雄捷運表示有意跟進，專家則說，公廁限時是趨勢，這是大數據運算的結果。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵也有公廁限時機制，高鐵站的無障礙廁所有「四分鐘警報」設計，<span class=\"red\">當使用者維持同一姿勢超過四分鐘靜止不動時，廁所內感應器就會啟動警報</span>，通知站務人員前往查看。對此高鐵表示，這麼設定是基於4-6分鐘的黃金救援時間，所以只要民眾有動作，就不用擔心時間限制。"},{"pid":"8cf053396ea2350399517da5e08c034d2de4e425","tid":2311880,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f616cad138055edd9eddccccfe27839ddf1ce319","tid":2311880,"uid":1654,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"扑野唔怕"},{"pid":"31f4884d283c4200181eedff36da063e9c33f10a","tid":2311880,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"係屎塔放鬆下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53686dda710a92372d11452de1a5d9176d7afcfa","tid":2311880,"uid":301050,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"31f4884d283c4200181eedff36da063e9c33f10a","tid":2311880,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"係屎塔放鬆下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"舊屎出緊但係一過4分鐘就響<br />\n嚇到縮返入去"},{"pid":"d4102d8dc50443d800a32c72ebe1fcc05a967a13","tid":2311880,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"lunch 咪無得係廁所開飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6019dbe302387d79801f1d563b8beac864fbce6f","tid":2311880,"uid":62950,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"我痾屎要20分鐘 痾到15分鐘有人拍門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6647926e2385de520147c071f9ab61bbffb2ac88","tid":2311880,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53686dda710a92372d11452de1a5d9176d7afcfa","tid":2311880,"uid":301050,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"31f4884d283c4200181eedff36da063e9c33f10a","tid":2311880,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"係屎塔放鬆下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"舊屎出緊但係一過4分鐘就響<br />\n嚇到縮返入去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"唔郁先4 分鐘<br />\nkeep 住Coincidance唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f2810bf152ff48e0e9e569fe71a01074f4d2e0","tid":2311880,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6647926e2385de520147c071f9ab61bbffb2ac88","tid":2311880,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53686dda710a92372d11452de1a5d9176d7afcfa","tid":2311880,"uid":301050,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"31f4884d283c4200181eedff36da063e9c33f10a","tid":2311880,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"係屎塔放鬆下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"舊屎出緊但係一過4分鐘就響<br />\n嚇到縮返入去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"唔郁先4 分鐘<br />\nkeep 住Coincidance唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"時間管理大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b4b2de5165e61f114ad8a28641855cbf9cf2f2","tid":2311880,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"大陸廁所 都有限時 <br />\n<br />\n仲限埋廁紙Tim"},{"pid":"bfb0a0a41e8fa283270b97a513744909375b8a00","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39b4b2de5165e61f114ad8a28641855cbf9cf2f2","tid":2311880,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"大陸廁所 都有限時 <br />\n<br />\n仲限埋廁紙Tim"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"上海市近來也推出「智能公廁」，除了求救鈴也有警報器，使用者待超過十五分鐘，警報會自動響起，讓清潔人員前往關心。據報導，確曾遇過老人因腿部痠麻站不起來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c237f0d0b38a8d3f05e9b4cd95d9b1026ccfb2","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"超過15分鐘將有站務人員關心，若逗留30分鐘以上，警報器就會大聲作響，北捷指出，這項關心機制源於，交通尖峰或跨年期間，因捷運運量大，乘客常抱怨某一廁間使用太久，並強調偵測時間也是一種關心機制，若遇有旅客身體不適情況，可以及時提供協助，雖立意良善，但也有民眾認為，被關心上廁所時間有點壓力。<br />\n<br />\n民眾:「就是像一些會便祕的人，想要上廁所，然後可是15分鐘可能會不夠，所以就是會緊張，怕15分鐘沒有上出來，就是會響，就是會有人來關心。」「我覺得還不錯啊，如果被困在廁所，都沒人發現的話，還蠻危險的，(關心)應該還好吧我覺得，就是再應個門跟他說沒事就好了。」「因為15分鐘來講，應該是對一般人來講都很足夠了，車站這裡本來就是，一堆治安的死角，這種(機制)應該是對於安全，對什麼的有不小的幫助。」"},{"pid":"d895f00d320c3e3bf07e1164bac7d81fa92aa7e0","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/05/27/920667-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F920667-PH.jpg&h=5a2a4b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名網友在批踢踢實業坊以「在捷運上廁所太久，會被工作人員關切」為題發文，他透露自己在捷運車站內上廁所，知道後面沒有人排隊，隔壁間也沒有人在使用，因此在過程中也使用了手機，時間大概20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n「一沖水打開門，外面有義交（應為捷運保全）跟清潔媽媽在等！」上完廁所推開門見到這個陣仗，讓原PO也好奇問說：「是上太久嗎？」而清潔媽媽則說「對啊」，一旁的保全也彷彿鬆了一口氣。"},{"pid":"0642cc45a8bbaec0dc9593014a9aa7168b6d453c","tid":2311880,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6019dbe302387d79801f1d563b8beac864fbce6f","tid":2311880,"uid":62950,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"我痾屎要20分鐘 痾到15分鐘有人拍門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"便秘問題幾嚴重 快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"752d35c4565eb3858f61a9b7c7ad597131a03eb6","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0642cc45a8bbaec0dc9593014a9aa7168b6d453c","tid":2311880,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6019dbe302387d79801f1d563b8beac864fbce6f","tid":2311880,"uid":62950,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"我痾屎要20分鐘 痾到15分鐘有人拍門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"便秘問題幾嚴重 快啲睇醫生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常係幾分鐘？"},{"pid":"8cd6105f6cdd716a697524314f31edfb7b7caf64","tid":2311880,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"平時返工鍾意去廁所睇股票，打機，上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a386cde1a8dd0d0cdbfad6d131210a61a95495e4","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53686dda710a92372d11452de1a5d9176d7afcfa","tid":2311880,"uid":301050,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"31f4884d283c4200181eedff36da063e9c33f10a","tid":2311880,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"係屎塔放鬆下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"舊屎出緊但係一過4分鐘就響<br />\n嚇到縮返入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"一路柯一路郁"},{"pid":"870b56194d27127a619a755c3d57b73f45558a70","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755eb138112215decfcc37626b88cd38e1b22020","tid":2311880,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d4102d8dc50443d800a32c72ebe1fcc05a967a13","tid":2311880,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"lunch 咪無得係廁所開飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}